headline: A New Generation of Renovators Is On the Rise: New CRAFTSMAN速 Survey Finds, Despite Uncertainty, Younger DIYers Feel Confident, Motivated to Accomplish Home Improvement Projects This Year

Rather than waiting or compromising, many Millennials and Gen Zers are rolling up their sleeves and literally taking matters into their own hands, according to newly released research from CRAFTSMAN速, the most trusted and recommended brand in Tools & Outdoor* for today's DIYers.
